$ cat /proc/interrupts | grep i8042
  1:       2081          XT-PIC  i8042

Whenever I attached the barcode reader to my linux box, interrupt handler
for i8042 has been activated. To read the signal, I'll have to install my
custom interrupt handler.


Search for 'i8042' online for programming it.

